    ],
    "ron_burgundy_voice": "Well, well, well, look at these fine athletes engaging in what appears to be a highly sophisticated game of pickleball. They're hitting a small ball back and forth over a net. It's quite\u2026 riveting. Stay classy, San Diego.",
    "chuck_norris_voice": "Chuck Norris doesn't play pickleball; pickleball plays him. And even then, he lets the ball win sometimes, just to keep things interesting.",
    "color_commentator_banter": "You know, I've seen some dink rallies in my day, but this one is something special. It's like watching a chess match, but with paddles. I'm just waiting for one of them to make a move, you know? A little flick of the wrist, a subtle change of pace...",
